# Untitled Visual Novel Game

## Repository
https://github.com/clovikei/Chloe-Choi-ANGM-2305-Final 

## Description
A short visual novel with a narrative effected by player's choice using pygame.

## Features
- Character sprite and background art
	- Sprites and background change based on narrative
- Choice Matters
	- Player choice directly effects narrative outcome. They will have clickable boxes.
- Sound effects
	- Text sfx and ambient music plays.
  -Possible point and click mechanic
   -Mouse clicks further narrative progression.

## Challenges
- I am unfamilar with making visual novels with pygame outside of ren'py, I will need to learn more.
- How to implement player choice.
- I have not made a game solo before.

